title: Sloco
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sandwich shop offers local, organic, and quick food. Has several vegan choices such as a quinoa-meatball sub and in-house-made seitan sub. All sandwiches can be made vegan or vegetarian. Shares seating space with a local art studio.
